      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 30,
      "message": "Hi Ramesh,\n\nI came across this patch while looking for another AAF bug.\nI second what Sylvain says regarding your use of templates here. Nice work.\n\nJust an FYI, there may be a case for a ready.py checek for aaf-service before running the aaf-agent image.\nhttps://jira.onap.org/browse/DMAAP-1388\nWe ran into issues where AAF wasn't fully up so may be something to be aware of.\n\nThanks,\nFiachra",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 4405,
        "name": "Fiachra Corcoran",
        "display_name": "Fiachra Corcoran (EST)",
        "email": "fiachra.corcoran@est.tech",
